<br>
Not boring as other spawn camps either.  There always seems to be a wander the shows up when you low on mana, or a level 40 spider or wolffie wanders past.  Even with a 200 int and focus items there always seems to be a spawn ready when I would mana up.<br>
<br>
After I hit 44 I plan to visit Sol B to get the rest of my research items for the other three pets, then I will try the Glacier Yeti.<br>
<br>
<br>
Good hunting<br>
<br>
Zolac<br>
