<br>
I went back there tonight for a little bit and found that with a little care you can easily own the entire cave.  That is all 7 static spawns plus the 2 or 3 that wander.  I left soon after though as I was asked to join a guild group in Karnors and it was pretty boring controlling the entire place.<br>
